omg i just got back from mandies house and she showed me the saddest movie thing ever! like it was about animals getting slautered!! and it showed what they did and stuff and omg its so awful! i am so goin vegiterian now.  plus by the looks of it, it doesnt seem all that sanitery neways.  my new goal/thing i wanna do before i die, is to go to atleast 5 slauter houses and bomb them! the animals were goin to die ne ways, so i feel bad for them, but i wanna kill of of the mother fuckers who can seriously do that to an animal. they are terrible people and ya.  and to there family's who are like omg my husband, brother, sister, mother or w/e died!! ahh how could someone bomb that place??!!?? or w/e they choose to say, well they can all rot in hell too! cause there help supporting it! but if you wanna see it, then its in my profile that says burger, so check it out!!

well we found this dog on saterday.  it is the sweetest dog you could ever meet.  it listens so well and is just so awsome.  when we found it, it was super skinny and you could tell that the owners before didnt take good care of it.  and if you ask me, then they should die and go to hell!!.. i want them to live an eternity of sorrow and pain.  they need to have a slow painful death!! ne one who treats a dog that bad should be shot!.  but ne ways..my mom said that she doesnt want a dog that big and w/e. and we cant bring it inside cause of how bad it smells and it looks so helpless.  my dad is being such an ass about it too.  he is the only one who dosent show ne sympathy towards it.  all this morning i have been so upset over the thing.  i want it so bad cause it looks so sad and helpless.  i hate how this always seems to happen....

whoo its finilly new years which means its finily time to go back to school! im way ready, my house gets old after awhile. but yes, i havent came up with any real new years resolutions...im still thinkin of them.  alicia is over right now..i think shes sick though, wow it sucks but its nice to just have her around.  but ne ways.....i went to downtown fredericksburg for new years eve.  it was ok besides the fact that i felt really sick.  but we saw alot of people there. there was alan, kent, tippie, kelsie, victoria, matt, noah, holly, emily, brandon...and thats all i can think of right now.  it was cold there though.  but the bar-b-q was good..lol.  wel i must go now.  have a happy new years!!!!!
~~05!!! we finilly made it!!!~~

--ariel(sp-maybe):-)

o man o man o man!!!
